title: Cant launch lol on mac
body: I quit lol in a game before the match started. Now where ever i try to open it says there is already another copy open do you want to terminate. Then it does nothing i can't to anything about this please help me with advice on how to fix this.

replies.body:
Hey there,

Have you tried restarting your computer? Sounds like there's still an active copy of the game/launcher running on your computer and this would be the easiest way to kill that process.
I just tried snd it fixed my problem thanks lots

Good to hear your issue was resolved.

See you on the Rift,
Seph
